{
  "stem": "13524.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Polish policemens were-- you know, they didn't really try to shoot or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was not that severely guarded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And later on, I have devised a method of taking my kennkarte Ausweis, the things that-- like a pass-- and put some money in between, and open to identify myself to the Polish policeman, give him some money.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He took the money nicely, put it in his pocket, and winked to the German soldier to let me out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I even had the audacity to ask, till what time are you on duty, so that I had access back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because I really felt there is nowhere for me to stay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I think when one is so young, one doesn't stop to consider the danger one is in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I often used to bring to ghetto-- I was the source of bringing potatoes, carrots, a bit-- whatever bit of bread, whatever I could buy.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there were ration cards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was not adequate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we had means.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And certainly, who had still a little bit of money, or a ring, or a brooch, you could exchange.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were people who were bringing oil, flour, into the ghetto, illegally.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it did exist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But one had to pay for it dearly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we certainly have not been so well off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were very much middle class.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we did not accumulate money, or jewelry, or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My mother had sheets, pillowcases, towels.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And with that was good enough to procure some food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the beginning, it sort of-- non-- non-- event.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But later on, the SS used to come and just-- didn't like somebody, they would shoot them.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
